Where do all the clusters map in Cluster 3?

Load libraries.

library(Seurat)
library(tidyverse)
library(RColorBrewer)

Load umap of cluster.

load("/Volumes/all_ssd/20220414-seurat/flox-integr-res-0.0120/flox-3-res-0.025/umap-by-cluster-flox-3-res-0.025.Robj")
umap.3 <- clust.umap
umap.3$cluster.cluster <- as.character(clust.umap$cluster.cluster)
head(umap.3)
table(umap.3$cluster.cluster)

 3.1  3.2 
4219 3075

Load umap of subclusters.

load("/Volumes/all_ssd/20220414-seurat/flox-integr-res-0.0120/flox-3-res-0.025/flox-3.1-res-0.0387/umap-by-cluster-flox-3.1-res-0.0387.Robj")
umap.3.1 <- clust.umap

Recode cluster into subclusters.

umap.3[as.vector(rownames(umap.3.1 %>% filter(cluster.subclust == "3.1.1"))), "cluster.cluster"] <- "3.1.1"
umap.3[as.vector(rownames(umap.3.1 %>% filter(cluster.subclust == "3.1.2"))), "cluster.cluster"] <- "3.1.2"
umap.3[as.vector(rownames(umap.3.1 %>% filter(cluster.subclust == "3.1.3"))), "cluster.cluster"] <- "3.1.3"
umap.3$cluster.cluster <- factor(umap.3$cluster.cluster, levels = c("3.1.1", "3.1.2", "3.1.3", "3.2"))
table(umap.3$cluster.cluster)

3.1.1 3.1.2 3.1.3   3.2 
 2557  1089   573  3075

Generate label umap.

umap.label <- umap.3 %>% group_by(cluster.cluster) %>% summarize(umap.1 = median(umap.1), umap.2 = median(umap.2))

Generate cluster umap.

cluster.umap <- ggplot() +
geom_point(data = sample(umap.3), mapping = aes(x = umap.1, y = umap.2, color = cluster.cluster), shape = 20, stroke = 0, size = 0.5) +
geom_text(data = umap.label, mapping = aes(x = umap.1, y = umap.2, label = cluster.cluster), size = 2.3) +
labs(title = "Cluster 3, Nipbl Flox/+", x = "UMAP 1", y = "UMAP 2", color = "Cluster") +
  guides(color = guide_legend(override.aes = list(size = 2.4))) +
theme_classic(base_size = 7) +
theme(axis.line = element_blank(), axis.ticks = element_blank(), axis.text = element_blank(), plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, size = 7), legend.key.size = unit(7, "pt"))
cluster.umap

clust.umap <- umap.3
save(clust.umap, file = "/Volumes/all_ssd/20220414-seurat/flox-integr-res-0.0120/flox-3-res-0.025/umap-by-cluster-flox-3-res-0.025-4.Robj")
ggsave(plot = cluster.umap, filename = "/Volumes/all_ssd/20220414-seurat/flox-integr-res-0.0120/flox-3-res-0.025/umap-by-cluster-flox-3-res-0.025-4.png", device = "png", width = 3.5, height = 2.25, units = "in")
